# 🚀 Solusi Optimasi (Sangat Penting)

## 1️⃣ Aktifkan Code Splitting di Vite

Edit **vite.config.ts**

```ts
export default defineConfig({
  build: {
    rollupOptions: {
      output: {
        manualChunks: {
          react: ["react", "react-dom"],
          supabase: ["@supabase/supabase-js"],
        }
      }
    }
  }
})
```

Ini bisa mengurangi vendor JS sampai **40%**

---

# 🚀 2️⃣ Lazy Load Halaman

Contoh salah:

```tsx
import Dashboard from "./pages/Dashboard"
```

Perbaiki:

```tsx
const Dashboard = lazy(() => import("./pages/Dashboard"))
```

Dan gunakan:

```tsx
<Suspense fallback={<Loading/>}>
```

Ini bisa menaikkan performa **+20 skor Lighthouse**.

---

# 🚀 3️⃣ Aktifkan Tree Shaking

Pastikan:

```json
package.json
```

ada:

```json
"sideEffects": false
```

---

# 🚀 4️⃣ Optimasi Tailwind

Di file:

```
tailwind.config.js
```

Pastikan:

```js
content: [
"./index.html",
"./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}"
]
```

Ini akan menghapus CSS yang tidak dipakai.

